imdb.plot outline: Gabriel is a non such a normal boy and he has a deep obsession with La Antarctica and its scientific researches that are held in the "Estacion Pedro Vicente Maldonado" of Ecuador. Gabriel will live several daily experiences that will then merge with these researches that are done precisely for that, so that people like him and people like us live a little bit better in this planet.
